name: NEW CABIN! WestJet 737-600 Premium Vancouver to Calgary
description:
WestJet has been quietly storing its fleet of Boeing 737-600s in Marana, Arizona, over the past few months. Before this though, they reconfigured a single 737-600 with their new cabin that's now standard on the rest of their 737s - and I had the chance to fly it back in August last year!
